node.title: Omicron cluster grows as health authorities investigate Western Sydney indoor gym
node.description: Health authorities are conducting urgent genomic sequencing on 10 cases, part of a cluster at a western Sydney school. Three of the 13 cases are confirmed as the Omicron strain.
node.content:
["NSW Health authorities are focusing their investigation on\u00a0a\u00a0Sydney indoor climbing gym as\u00a0the number\u00a0of Omicron cases grows.\u00a0", "The gym was visited\u00a0by\u00a0a group of school students from the Regents Park Christian School, which has 13 cases of COVID-19, three\u00a0confirmed as\u00a0the Omicron variant.", "Urgent testing is underway on the remaining 10.\u00a0", "Anyone who was at the gym on Saturday, November 27\u00a0between 9am and 4.30pm is considered a close contact and must get tested and isolate for seven days.\u00a0", "A student who had not been overseas and had no links to anyone who had was confirmed as the school's first case on Thursday.", "Health authorities fear this is a sign the Omicron COVID-19 variant is spreading in the community, with\u00a0a total of 13 cases\u00a0with the variant in NSW.", "The western Sydney school has now been closed for the rest of the year and all staff and students have been identified as close contacts.", "NSW\u00a0has recorded 325 new locally acquired COVID-19 cases, and a woman aged in her 50s from south-western Sydney has\u00a0died at Liverpool Hospital.", "The woman was\u00a0fully vaccinated but had underlying health conditions, NSW Health confirmed.", "NSW Health said 94.6 per cent of people aged 16 and over have received a first dose of a COVID-19 vaccine, and 92.7 per cent are fully vaccinated.", "Almost 70,000 people were tested\u00a0to 8pm last night,\u00a0compared with 80,930 on the previous day.", "", "
NSW students being tested for Omicron
", "Yesterday Health Minister Brad Hazzard said the outbreak was concerning, as the virus appeared\u00a0to have been transmitted in the community.", "\"I think transmission is always a concern but we\u00a0need to keep it in perspective at the moment,\" he said.", "\"Worldwide, there is not clarity around whether this particular variant is going to cause us anywhere near the problems that the earlier variants caused us.\"", "Two new\u00a0cases in returned travellers who were confirmed\u00a0to be affected by the Omicron variant\u00a0were the parents of a child with the variant.", "The family\u00a0travelled\u00a0on Qatar Airways flight QR908 from Doha to Sydney on November 23.", "The family had not travelled to southern Africa,\u00a0prompting NSW Health to suspect transmission occurred on the flight.", "A number of venues visited by the family in Chatswood on Sydney's lower north shore have been listed as\u00a0exposure sites.", "Three\u00a0Omicron cases have been identified in passengers on a flight from Singapore to Sydney on November 28.", "Every person who was on the Singapore Airlines flight has been asked to get tested immediately and isolate until they receive a negative result.", "Positive Omicron cases have also been identified in passengers on\u00a0two other Qatar Airways flights from Doha, which landed on November 25 and 27 respectively.", "Anyone who has\u00a0been\u00a0in South Africa, Lesotho, Botswana, Zimbabwe, Mozambique, Namibia, Eswatini and Malawi 14-days before arriving\u00a0in NSW must go into\u00a0hotel quarantine for 14 days, irrespective of their\u00a0vaccination.", "Those who have visited\u00a0any of the eight African countries within the previous 14 days must\u00a0get tested and isolate for 14 days, and call NSW Health.", "", "
Heavily mutated Omicron variant puts scientist on alert
"]
